These are some scripts for sending content to my Kindle.

To work, you need to have "mutt" installed and configured, following:

  http://blog.nguyenvq.com/2010/07/10/how-to-set-up-sending-mail-from-the-command-line/


And you need to put the scripts in a place where they can be found, such as /usr/local/bin

PS: I am using Ubuntu 10.10

Adolfo Neto
September 14th, 2011.
